            using Google's OAuth authorization process. We access email content, metadata, and attachments
            solely to process finance-related messages on your behalf.
          </p>
          <p>We do not sell, share, or use Gmail data for advertising purposes.</p>
          <p>Access tokens are stored securely and encrypted. Email data is processed only to provide the service requested by the user.</p>
          <p>You can revoke Lumoâ€™s access at any time by disconnecting your account in the Lumo app or via your Google Account security settings.</p>
          <p>
            For questions, contact:
            <a class="text-white hover:text-lumo-brand transition-colors" href="mailto:suporte@lumoai.com.br">
              suporte@lumoai.com.br
